body:
I recently picked up Vi and she&#039;s been a ton of fun. However, the idea of Bloodrazor into Cleaver into full tank has popped into my mind a few times. I haven&#039;t tried it out of fear of it being garbage and have been doing okay with just Warrior enchant. 

However, one game I went against this fed Darius. He was nearly impossible to kill. Admittedly I probably should&#039;ve ganked more for my top laner but, after that game the thought has been really bugging me. Part of me kept saying &quot;Could&#039;ve won if you just maxed W and went BloodRazor&quot;

But, anyway. Is it viable?
